# <type>(<scope>): <subject>  [max 72 chars]
# │       │           │
# │       │           └─ imperative, lowercase, no period
# │       └─ optional: api|shared|domain|infra|worker|crawl|gold|dbt|docker|ci
# └─ feat|fix|docs|style|refactor|perf|test|build|ci|chore|revert
#
# Body: explain WHY, not WHAT. Wrap at 100 chars.
# Break after 72 chars in subject.
#
# Examples:
#   feat(api): implement cursor pagination for enriched posts
#   fix(worker): narrow exception catch to domain error types
#   ci: install all extras in type-check job for mypy stub resolution
#   test(gold): add integration tests for incremental build tracking
